Kya aapko pata hai duniya ki sbse tezz chalne waali train wheels pr nahi hawa me chalti hai aur iss train ki maximum speed 603 KMPH hai jo ki world's highest train speed record hai 

Hello Dosto, aaj ki iss video me hum, japan ki MAGLEV train ke baare me jaanenge jo ki railway tracks se 10 centimeter jo ki 4 inch k lagbhag hota hai lavitate krti hai iss levitation ki wajah 
se hi ye train technology itna high speed achieve krne me successful ho paayi hai 

Iss trains ka development pehli bar 20 century me propose kiya gaya tha aur time ke saath saath technical advancement ne inn trains ko possible bnaya hai aur iss par research ki ja rahi hai jisse inn 
technology ko aur bhi advance aur efficient banaya ja sake.

MAGLEV ka full form Magnatic levitation hai ki train ko track ke upper float krne k liye allow krta hai aur ye normal trains ke comparisons me completely different technology hai to tracks aur 
wheelset k relative motion se chalti hai inn trains ka successful trial japan ne 1972 me kiya tha

Japan me MAGLEV trains me Super COnducting Magnets ka use kiya jata hai isliye inhe SCMaglev kehta hai 

iss train k magnets ek bar exciting current se charge hone par ye magnets bht strong magnetic field generate karte hai 

inn magnetic leviatated trains ko functional krne k liye mainly  three challenges achieve krne padhte hai 1. PROPEL 2. LAVITATE 3. GUIDANCE 

inn trains ka principle magnets ki polar properties par completely depend krta hai, jab hum magnets k similar poles ko pass laate hai to magnets ek repulsive force form krte hai aur 
agar hum opposite poles ko pass laaye to magnets attractive force generate krte hai aur ek dusre se chipak jaate hai aur isi magnet property ka application ye MAGLEV trains hai

Agar inn magnets ka temparature kam se kam kr diya jaye to magnets ka material kam se kam electrical resistance offer krega jisme current flow krne par bht strong magnetic force generate hoga 
aur kamk se kam losses honge, inn trains k super conducting magnets ko sirf ek bar excite krne ki jrurt hoti hai uske bad ye bht time tak kaam kr skte hai, lekin inhe kam se kam temperature par maintain
krna hota hai jiske liye liquid helium refrigeratation system ka use kiya jata hai 

SCMaglev trains ke superconducting magnet me Niobium-Titanium (Nb-Ti) alloy hota hai jiska critical temperature âˆ’263.95Â°ğ¶ ya 9.2 K ke barabar hota hai, iss temperature ko maintain krne k liye liquid 
helium ko âˆ’268.95Â°ğ¶ ya 4.2 K per in magnet pr circulate kiya jata hai.

conductive radiation se bachne k liye inn super conductive magnets ko radiation shield me rkha jata hai jisme complete vaccumm hota hai 
aur iss radiation shield ko liquid nitrogen se kam temperature ko maintain kiya jata hai 

ese 4 super conductor magnets ko 1 unit me align kiya jata hai aur trains k dono taraf sets me lgaya jata hai aur ye magnets bina electricity ke kaamm krte hai 

Inn trains ko propel krne ke liye propelling coil ka use kiya jata hai jisme alternating tarike se power supply kkiya jata hai aur inn propelling coils ko guideway ke andar place kiya jata hai 
train ko aage badhaane k liye, propelling coil me superconductive magnets ke opposite magnetic force generate kiya jata hai jiske net force se train ka movement hota hai
jaise hi train aage badhti hai to propelling coil ki polarity switch kr di jati hai jisse train ki speed ek direction me badhti jaati hai aur train ki speed ko switching frequency ko control krke ki 
ja sakti h

MAGLEV trains ke liye dusra challenge lavitatation hai jise engineers ne faraday's k law ki help se achieve kiya hai, Inn super conductor magnets ka pair ek single unit MAGNET ki tarah behave krta hai 
Engineers ne guideway me 8 shaped coils ko install kiya hai, jab train propell krti hai super conducting magnets in 8 shaped coils me EMF induce hota hai aur train k propel hone se ek net upward force 
generate hota hai jisse train me levitation achieve hota hai train ki speed jitni hogi utna hi levitation achieve hoga, ye levivation khadi train me kaam nahi karta hai isliye inn trains ki low speed me 
normal wheels ka use kiya jata hai 

-----------
iss train ka next challenge guidance hai aur iss train ko guideway se takraye bina chalna chahiye iss challenge ko overcome krne k liye engineers ne 8 shaped coils ko interconnect kr diya hai,

jab train guideway k centre m hoti hai to train k dono taraf guideway me induced EMF equal hota hai, agr train guideway ki taraf jaane ki koshish krti hai to super conductors in 8 shaped coil me EMF 
difference generate krte hai aur train pr lateral net magnetic force produce hota hai jo train ko guideway k center me laata hai jisse ye maglev train high speed me bhi safe ban jaati hai

Maglev trains high speed up to 600KMPH tk achieve kr skti hai jo ki tradiotionally use hone waali trains se bht jyada hai inn trains e magnects ke use hone se magnetic 
cushion generate hota hai jisse riding experience bht jyada badh jata hai inn trains me kam moving parts hote hai jisse maintenance bhi kam hota hai aur inki effieciency bht jyada hoti h

iss khubiyo k alava inn trains k kuchh nuksaan bhi hai inhe banane ki cots bht jyada hai aur inkn trains ke liye separately infrastructure bnana 
pdta hai isske saath saath inn trains ko operate krneme bht jyada energy consumption hota hai 
